\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 He were very - straight and very good but very strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Your mother was an easy person to talk to then was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, she was a good person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When you say a good person, in what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - she used to shield us. And she were good to anybody - that were - sick, you
 know, she couldn't afford to take 'em a lot but - she were always - I know me older sisters used to have lock door sometimes - so she wouldn't go out to stop up all night with people. You know. She was so - she were a kind person were my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did she show affection to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, she were a good - she were a good mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If you had any worries could you share them with your mother or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I don't remember ever having any but - if I had I could have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You say your father was very strict?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh, very strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Could you talk to him at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so, I don't think I - I could have told me father anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he ever show any affection to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - he did in his way. But - he were ve
ry - you know, were very strict in a lot of ways. We couldn't read a paper. Or read - cheap books or - anything like that. Oh he - he were a good father, but very strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If you had any worries then you wouldn't tell them to your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well we were obedient as you might say. We never brought 'em any trouble home. And there were nine of us, so - we - they'd nothing to worry about in that line.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways, how did they tell you to behave to each other?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, I think we agreed very well, but I've one sister - that were different from all of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Which one was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 She'd a 
very hasty temper. But I - I can see her now and I think about her when I'm by myself a lot. She were never well. But - she had a terrible temper. She'd throw anything at you. You know, she were - and me brothers used to hit her, and me father did. I can 
e
ver remember me father hitting any of us, only her. But this one sister - but she died when she were forty-seven. She died very sudden. But she were a sufferer. She had a - a bad chest. And she's the only one that's ever - ailed anything in all of life. B
ut this one sister - next younger than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I never remember 'em doing. Never remember her saying so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well they always - brought us up to be honest and impressed on us - never to touch anything that didn't belong to us. I can - me father I today I can see him, you know, when - they used to bring their homework home - from work - to prepa
re for morning after, thread the needles and that. Every bit of thread had to go back. You - you know, nothing had to be left at home. He were very honest and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents bring you up to consider anything else important in life, what other things did they consider important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well for being - just honest and clean. In us - habits and all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we were never allowed to hear any swearing in the house. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Not if it was anything - that we shouldn't hear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You hadn't to talk at mealtimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If you did something your parents disapproved of what would happen, you only remember your sister being thrashed don't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't think - we were ever - any trouble in that way, to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you ever remember being punished at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, not - not to - remember. But I can always remember - I can see me father -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did he do to her, what did he smack her with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 He always had a belt. He had a belt. I can see that belt now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And you only remember him using it on that one sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your mother ever smack this sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would you say you
 received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents, or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I think they were both.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When you had a birthday would it be any different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, she always - mother always tried to put a jelly or something different on. Yes, she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you receive any presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any guests in for tea, did you have any little friends in for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, not a lot but - there were such a lot of us own. Yes. 'Cos the older ones'd be older then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Can you remember anything you did with your mother or father together on Christmas Day, what happened on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we'd always - a nice Christmas Day and always a Christmas }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 treat}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 . Yes. And we - and we'd always toys. We hadn't a lot - expensive ones, but we'd always toys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever play games together at Christmas or make music, anything else you remember about Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, we used to have a - a nice - meals, we'd always - good meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only - only mouth organ and - you know - little - not expensive -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who played the mouth organ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Our Charlie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was he a good player?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes he were. He were a good lad were Charlie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Our Charlie used to do. And whistle. He were right good whistler. Charlie, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Enough to entertain you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes, he used to - you know he used to - pull blind down and make things with his fingers - he were right good were our Charlie.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Quite an entertainer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes? He were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever make music together as a family, did you have a sing-song or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - we had but not - not - often like, didn't happen -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever sing when he played the mouth organ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I could never sing - I could never sing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you dance when he played the mouth organ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. I could never sing. No, I can't sing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did - who? No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Any games outside did they play with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, me father used to go to pub every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he go nearly every night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 It were very near.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Books? Well I don't remember a many.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there any newspapers or magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, but we weren't - children weren't allowed to look at papers in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 He were frightened of us - reading something we shouldn't do. But we used to read 'em and hide 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where did you used to hide them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 At back - I used to put mine at back of gas oven - gas meter on a high shelf.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of books were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well they were love stories and them, you know. So we daren't let me father see 'em. My mother saw 'em but my father didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember your mother reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Could she read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I don't think she were a good reader but she didn't read, I don't think she had time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so. He read the papers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they ever read aloud to you or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember a funeral in the family before the end of the first world war, before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 1918? Well me father'd be dead then. He died in about 1907 I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember anything about your father's funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Me father's funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I shouldn't be so old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember anything at all about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. I can remember him - dying. How old should I be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You'd be nineteen then wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Eighteen, yes, I should. Yes, I - I remember me father dying, he - he - of course he died in the infirmary, and he - it - it were a cancer on his stomach, but o
f course they didn't call 'em then. I don't know what they called it then. But he were only in the infirmary a week. And I remember him dying.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Anything at all you remember about the funeral, did you go to the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, I went to the funeral
, and always remember - 'cos me sisters were married then. And all their husbands were bearers. You know, at the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of clothes did you all wear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we were all in black. And then mauve. Then grey - grey and then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long did you wear black for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh twelve month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long mauve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And then it were mourning and went - I - I remember we were in - of course in them days they did go - they did wear mourning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 So after you'd finished wearing black you wore mauve did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Either mauve or grey, I've just forgot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was it a motor carriage or a horse carriage that took your father, did you remember anything about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I think it were a - a horse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relations, did you ever go visiting anybody as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - we used to visit - me sisters that were married. You know, they were married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they live round about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, they all lived round about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever visit neighbours at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, I - we - some good neighbours. I - I used to go errands for one, eeh and she did buy me some nice things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever visit any other relations apart from your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't think we had a lot of relations, we had some - 
we used to - they used to visit from Manchester, and we used to go to Manchester. To - to visit them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who used to take you when you went visiting your sisters, did you go on your own or did someone take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, we went on us own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you ever taken shopping when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, my mother used to take us shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 Did you ever go out with just your father, you went to this Todmorden Fair didn't you? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Anywhere else you remember going with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I never remember going anywhere else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember any other outings with your parents, at Bank Holidays or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever go away for a holiday when you were a schoolchild?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Could you tell me how you spent S
aturdays in those days, what did you do on a Saturday? Do you remember doing anything special on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Not when I were young but when I were older I used to help in a tearooms. At Hebden bridge, at Park Castle Crags. I used to help in the tearooms at Saturday and Sunday and holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was this when you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When I was - oh no, when I had left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 This is up to you leaving school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, well I don't think - I don't think Saturday were any different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How about Sundays when you were a schoolchild, did anything happen on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you go to church at all or chapel?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, I - we used to go to - church on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was it Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, it were Roman Catholics. When we were right young. I don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were both your parents Catholics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No. 'Cos we weren't - we weren't really - Catholics but - we went mostly because us neighbours went. Children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You went with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But you weren't a proper Catholic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. But one of 'em - one of me parents were Catholics but I couldn't tell which now. But the other weren't. We weren't devoted Catholics.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How often did you go to church then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we used to go every Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How many times on the Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, either once or twice. When we were younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When did you stop going?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, when I were in me teens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you wear any different clothes on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we'd always us Sunday clothes, yes, we couldn't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 wear}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  them any other day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you allowed to play games on Sunday, did your parents think - it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 They didn't go to church?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You went once or twice on a Sunday when you were young to the Roman Catholic church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you go to a Sunday school or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, at - but we used to go to Sunday school at - Catholic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there any Sunday school outings, do you remember any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only Whitsuntide.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where would they go then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 We had a field day. You know, some buns - we had a cup of tea and a - currant bun. A currant - like - currant teacake.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where would you go for this, where would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Buy the church. In a field by the church. But I don't remember any other outings we had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What other social activities organised by the church did you take part in, did you belong to any clubs at the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Yes, we used to have - magic lantern - evenings. And - we had concerts. And we had - got concerts up. For the church. When we were younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you take part in them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well not - I were never very great at anything like that. I made one hymn. I made one hymn but - I weren't very great at -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, I couldn't sing. You know, I did a bit of acting and - but not - I weren't good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What was this magic lantern thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, we used to have a man - one
 night a week. It were all on - Bible or - or - you know, it were all - religion but it were - somewhere to go one night a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you belong to the choir?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did the church ran any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I don't think so. I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you belong to any other club organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was grace said at meals in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you taught to say your prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh - yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who taught you to say your prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you know what his views were, did he ever talk about the government?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 Yes, well if he did, he were a Liberal.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Why do you think he was a Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well I can - remember him - you know, once talking. But - I can't remember - but always remember - him being - there were only Liberal and Cons in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, she never took any interest in anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember - your father or mother voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from thei
r employers, do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure, to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was your father a member of the Liberal Party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you ever remember your father working for the Liberals at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father take part in any political activity other than at election times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time? Did your mother have any
 free time or was she too busy with all the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 She was too busy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did she have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No knitting or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father have any interests or hobbies apart from going to the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your mother have any interests at all outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And she never went out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What time did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I think it would be going on for six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How many evenings a week would he spend at home, did he ever stay in or did he go out to the pub each night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - he would stop at home some nights. But - sometimes he'd go back to mill. Yes. They went back to mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 To work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. He were very interested in his work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father attend any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. Only the pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How often did he go to the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say four - or five times a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your mother ever go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You say when he came home from the pub he wanted you to rec}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 ite}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 , can you tell me a bit more about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well he - he were always jolly. You know, and - and if he came home and we weren't in bed - if he bring somebody with him - he used t
o say, come on, recite. Say that recitation. And we used to do and he'd give us a penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he go to the pub on Sundays too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. But - at - in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he attend the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he bet?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so. Not - not to my knowledge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Any boot clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Sick club, funeral club or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did your mother manage when your father died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
I've often wondered that myself. 'Cos there were no pension. There were no pension then. And - there were only - I were the old - there were only - oh, the
re were me - and one brother at home. Two brothers at home. But one - worked at the Post office and he got transferred. And the other brother - came home from the war - invalid. And he didn't work for years. He got no pension.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And your mother didn't take a job when your father died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
No. No. I've wondered many a time how she did do. Because there were only - there were this brother that he didn't work you know. He ought to have had his leg off, he'd have had - very badly wounded. And then there we
re me. And then there were our Hettie, well she hardly never worked. Then our Florrie - yes, she started working when - that week me father died. So she'd be working, but we didn't earn much money then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters, you said you go on quite well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, weren't for this one sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was there any one you felt particularly close to, any one brother or sister you felt very close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I - I liked 'em all, they were - we - we got on well together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 As a child who did you play with? Did you play with your brothers and sisters or did you play with neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - we played with neighbours - children. And us own children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where did you play?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well there were - we lived on the roadside. But there was a field - across the road. And we played in there a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever play in other homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9250902\charrsid13597434 es.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
 WE used to in one another's homes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever play in your yard or garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we had a little garden but only a s
mall - we couldn't play in it. Had railings round. But - there were always somewhere to play. There were no playgrounds but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we played at keeping house and - all - well I couldn't tell you, all sorts of games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Anything you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only - I know we were very happy children as you might say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, we did do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents ever stop you from playing with any children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Not when I were young, but when I were in me teens - I were in the Primrose League.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 The Conservatives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What made you join the Conservatives if your father was a Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well I weren't politic - it weren't - it was merely - them what you went with. It weren't really - anything - that were - were a interested in politics or anything like that. It were just - as - 
them that you went pally with, you - you - went with 'em and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you do at the Primrose League?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we had meetings and social evenings and - played cards. Whist and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any hobbies when you were at school, how did you spent your free time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I - I don't remember having any hobbies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But I - I used to help - a lady that had a shop. She used to let me -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I hel
ped her - she had a little shop and I used to help her - you know, when anybody come in and she were in back, call over or - but she were very good to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did she used to pay you a bit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES? She were very good, she used to buy me clothes - you know, she'd buy me - pinafores and dresses and - she were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 very}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  good to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you collect anything, like stamps or pressed flowers or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever go for walks?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where did you used to walk round there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - were - were - some lovely walks in -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 It's lovely round there at Hebden Bridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9250902\charrsid13597434 es}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
. Oh yes, we used to go walks and gather bluebells and - in the woods. There were all woods round about. Some lovely walks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have a bike, did you ever go out on a bicycle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When you went for walks who did you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well there were generally some neighbours children or - me own sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever go to the theatres?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You said you went to concerts at the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever go to any other concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only at the other churches. We used to go to Church of England. I were brought up at Church of England school. Day school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever go to the music hall?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Or the cinema?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 There weren't any cinemas then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was your Sunday tea different from every day tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, we generally had a bit extra on a Sunday. We always - had either a tin of salmon or - or jelly or a bit of something extra.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any different supper on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No - I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - we didn't have much. It were only a copper. But - she used to buy sweets. And - when we went to school - you know, we just had - we didn't have money to spend. But we generally had a sweet or a bit of fruit. Not every day but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 So you didn't really have any pocket money then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after her house and family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Any relations, friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how did she manage? Did you ever remember your mother being ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. I just remember her when - the youngest - boy were born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember what happened when your younger brother was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I can remember him and the neighbours used to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 come}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  in and do for her then. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 In what ways did they help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - you see we had some older sisters - older - sisters at home, and they managed. But they looked after me
 mother and - saw that we were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What would the neighbours do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well the neighbours - helped and all. They - they came.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents have any relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your sisters live near when they got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But apart from that there was no one else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where were the nearest relatives to your parents, where did they live?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Manchester.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they see much of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, they did visit but - not to - not a l
ot. 'Cos they hadn't a lot of - relatives. I don't remember any of me father's, only - a cousin. But me mother had - two sisters. I can remember them, but they died when I were - young like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents have any friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - only - neigh
bours and - the families that me sisters all married in. They - they were all - same as one. They'd come - they came a lot 'cos they all - they'd all seemed to have - big families.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where did they see their friends, where did your parents meet their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - they visited one another's houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your mother and father share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't think me father ever bothered a lot but - me mother did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 So did your mother have friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only - same as - neighbours and relatives - and - and then families that me sisters married into.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father have friends just of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - only that men - not proper friends, only - casuals that he worked with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were friends ever invited into the home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - not to - not to spend a pleasant evening but just to visit. Just a call.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How often would that be that you had friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - not too often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, if it were once a week it be -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well not to drink but - I don't think I can remember 'em coming to a meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would they come in on any particular day or occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well it were mostly at weekends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would you say that the friends invited in were your mother's friends, your father's friends or friends of both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say - they were mostly father's friends. Or - fellows that he worked with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did friends call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well it's generally at the weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 They were mostly people that your father worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did neighbours call in without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When would neighbours come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, anytime of day. Every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents ever go out to visit friends or neighbours?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so. Not together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what do you think your parents did when 
they got together with friends or neighbours? Did they have music or play games or did they just talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I think they just talked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups, in that time before 1918 did you think of some p
eople belonging to one class and some to another? You }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 mentioned}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  that there were working class people round about didn't you?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there any other classes of people that you noticed in Hebden Bridge, what other different classes were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - not where we lived. They were all same as - there were nobody - what you might say - dirty or poor, but not well off. Just - week to week. Waiting of the wages as you might say. But - I don't think there were any - as we got - the children got
 up - grown up, it - they were all same as - willing to be a little bit better. But - none of 'em ever - got above their station as you might say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was there anybody else very poor at all anywhere in Hebden Bridge that you noticed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well there were plenty - there were plenty that were poor. You know, that lived in different - parts of Hebden Bridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What parts would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 They - more in the centre.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of occupations would the fathers have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well they'd all be - they'd
 be - in mill. You see - our family, we never went in mill, we never went half time. Never went in mill. They all went to a - you know, a proper - job as you might say. And job that you could - look to - after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 These were poor people in the mills were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 They -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were they woollen mills in Hebden Bridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Wool a-d cotton, they were both. But they were mostly - tailoring. A lot of - wholesale tailoring.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And that's what your family did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. And all my sisters, we all worked in - all the three oldest but - I never remember the oldest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were these very poor people not on full time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, they were and they weren't. They had short times - as well as full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there any people that were better off than you were that you noticed in Hebden Bridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, there were plenty a lot better off than us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - they had businesses and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Any others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And shops and - and good jobs in - in the firms where they worked for like, they'd all -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Which class would you say you belonged to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say a middle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of people belonged to the same class as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well what shall I say to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of jobs did they have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, a lot of 'em - had same jobs as - as us. You know, that - but I can't say that there's anybody that - that weren't }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 straight and}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  honest and - wanted to get on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of people belonged to the other classes, you said to the business class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 It was the people in the mills who were the very poor people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever come into these contact with these people who were very poor at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - yes, some of 'em had nice children. That were wanting to get o
ut of a - the groove that they'd been brought up. And we always tried to mix with 'em, and - we never - looked down on 'em as you might say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you ever told to curtsey or show respect in some way to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who would you curtsey to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well to the older people. Older than - more so the old people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have to show respect in any other way to people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only - be kind to 'em or run errands for 'em or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was there anyone you called sir or master or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - not sir but - the people that my father worked for - they brought my mother and father from Manchester with them. And we always - looked - they always looked on us and we - we called her madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was she an owner of a mill or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
But she were - they never looked down on us. They were very good to us. And they'd always - their family and our family - were always friends, when they were grown up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was it a mill that they owned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, a big - fustion mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did they do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - they made - you know, corduroy, they wove all that sort of stuff and - made the hole in between - the - the - in corduroy t
here's always - a mark up through isn't there and - well - they did - what they call - I don't know what they called it but - they used to make all sorts of fustion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And your father looked after the engines?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Oh yes, everybody did. Yes, they were well - respected. They weren't well off but we were - they - me father were very - and me mother and all were very - respected - with everybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't know, unless it were - because they were always nice to everybody. It weren't because we had anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 In the district where you lived in Hebden Bridge, who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should imagine the mill owners and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever come into contact with them, you came into contact with your father's employer didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES. Well that's all. And the - and when I got older - where I worked we were always friendly with the family that
 owned the business. But not - to go - visiting. But always at - you know, the first name. Always know one another's by us first name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Why do you think the mill owners were considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - with same as - the only thing I can see that we looked on 'em because they were finding us work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about the shopkeepers, who did they associate with, who did the shopkeepers have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I couldn't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about the clergy, who did they have for friends, did they mix with everybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Yes, I - I can remember the - the priest coming to our house. And if he came on a Friday they hadn't to have meat on a Friday. Frying pan were - if it were near dinner time there were always - frying pan with meat in it we 
had to hide it, Father's coming. Father - but he weren't a regular visitor but - if he came on a Friday - and he used to go round a lot on a Friday I think - to check up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who did the teachers have for friends, the schoolteachers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I don't know but they were all very nice. Can see 'em now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they mix with everybody or did they keep to themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, they - I know my teacher, I remember her, she went to church - and teached at Sunday school. She were a nice person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there any farmers round about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Farmers? Well - there were but not just - more on the hillsides.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who did they associate with, who did they have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I couldn't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And the employers, the mill owners and that, who did they have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well they'd have their own friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say them that were in business with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of people would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - both sorts. They were both - a lot
 of business folk went - they went to church. And so did - them that they employed. It were mixed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever notice what sort of people went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, it were same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where you lived did all the people in the working class have the sa
me standard of living or would you say there were different groups even within the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I thin-k they varied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 There were the poor people who worked in the mills?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes, well I don't know how they lived. I don't know how. 
I don't know how poor - them that I called poor folk, I don't know how they lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there just the two groups in the working class then, the poor ones and your own group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9250902\charrsid13597434 es}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 .

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you think that one group felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who? No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were some families thought of as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Which families would you call rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - the - even the respectable folk had - some children that were rough - as we
ll as the poor ones. Some made out good and some made out poor - in both sections.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever meet any rough people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think - there was none where we - just about where we lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers, was there a distinction between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they have the same attitude to people that were in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they treat them alike or differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so. I think they were - they were all alike to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Which class would she think she belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should - I should think - the middle class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Why do you think she thought of herself as belonging to the middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't th
ink she - I don't think she'd think anything about neither lower nor middle. I think - she was a - a very nice sensible woman, you know, that'd help anybody. Whether they were a - above her or below her.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You say you thought she thought of herself in 
the middle class, could this be because she was thinking of her parents, work, house or your father's job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Any particular reason why she'd consider she was sort of middle class? Could it be because of her own parents, work, th
e house you lived in or your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I think she were thinking of children. You know, wanting 'em - all to be - better in anything. Better theirself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another, can you remember }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 anyone}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  who sort of moved up the scale?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - as we got older they all seemed to - you know, majority of 'em seemed to - get on. You know, there weren't many that - didn't.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 With a big family once you started working it would be better wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Do you mean in the - oh yes, there were plenty. But I - I couldn't tell you who they were off hand but - there were plenty that - we looked up to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - same as - there were a big house not so far from us, and - at Christmas morning, we'd all to go - children went - wish 'em a Merry Christmas, and there were always a - a new penny and apple and orange, you know, a
nd - we always looked for - looked up to them. And - you know, they lived in a big house in it's own grounds. And all children used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 All the children from round about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 All - yes, round about - this big house, it wasn't so far off. But it w
ere - it weren't in our circle, you know, it was just across the row - across the fields. But it were a big house in its own grounds. My sister and me were only talking about it - last time she were here, when we used to go. At Christmas morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child? Did you ever see a policeman?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes. He used to walk - on his beat round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I think we were frightened of him as children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I don't know. It must have been - his uniform or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When you were naughty did your mother ever say, I'll call a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, it were always teacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How do you think the police treated the people, how did the policeman treat the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I never heard of anybody grumble about them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you see anything of the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, he came every - I don't if it were every week or every month for rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you feel about him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh he were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 All right in what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - we always paid rent and - he were always nice - with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember feeling that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well many a time, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you think about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes - we used to think that - we wish we were better off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What difference did it make to the family if your father was ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well he were never out of work until - the mill closed d
own. They - they closed down and it were about two year before he died. And then he - he weren't so well. And -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he get another job or was he out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I think he got a labourers job but - I don't know what it was now, it were - outs
ide, something outside. But he - then he - he started to be poorly and he died. He were only fifty-two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And you don't know how your mother managed then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember if you ever got help from the Guardians or the Parish or any charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 People didn't like to go in those days did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When there was someone in the district whom the people disapproved of very strongly was there any special way in which they showed it? }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 Do you remember anyone being made to move by rough music or anything like that?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You went to school didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, I went to Church of England school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When you first started what time in the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Every morn - every day, morning and afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What time would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Nine o'clock in morning. And - one o'clock at afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You went all day straight away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And it was a church school and it was a day school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was it for boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Mixed, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we hadn't - we didn't live so far off school. And I think we paid - tuppence a week. I - we paid a copper a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What was that for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
To go to school for books. Yes. But we could have gone to a free one. But it was farther away, but we went to the church school. Because it were near home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you walk there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, it weren't - so far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long would it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say ten minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well there were always some neighbours children and - and - and my own - sister and brothers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where did you have your midday meal, did you come home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 We went home. There were no school dinners - in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I think I always enjoyed school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You liked it then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, I liked them because they - they didn't - the teachers
 lived all near us. We knew them and knew their family. But they were all nice.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When your mother said she'd call a teacher if you were naughty how did you feel about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we didn't like to - think that we'd been naughty to - we didn't want teacher to know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important in life, like manners or tidiness or punctuality or ways of speaking? What did they teach you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 Well - I couldn't tell you, they - they liked cleanliness and they liked - obedience and - honesty.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How about punctuality, were you ever late?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes - oh I daresay I should be - oh I don't think I - I were ever late for school, but I were always late for work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about ways of speaking, did they help you with your speech at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I think they all spoke alike then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about manners, were they keen on good manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well you got caned.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did they cane you, on your hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, on - on - on your hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did the girls get the same punishment as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 For what sort of offences would you get the cane?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, being rude and - talking when you shouldn't do and - I don't think there was a lot you dare do. In them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes. They always wanted to know what we'd done and how we'd done.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they ever visit the school or meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well me mother might have done but me father never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, they were all - all classes went together. All - you know, from - from different homes, and different surroundings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have some of these poor children at your school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, they all went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 teacher\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you go to another school or did you always stay at this one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I stayed at the same school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I think I should be thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well not at - I don't think at that school I should have to go to another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You left school at thirteen, did you attend any part time education afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, not really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I've no regrets really. You know, I - I - I wer
en't a head girl but - I were an average - I weren't head or anything like that but - I - I always managed to - get through some way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 While you were at school did you ever have a part time job or any means or earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only just - going errands for neighbours. I were always very good - at going errands and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they pay you for that?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, if they didn't pay me in actual wage - they bought me things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Like the lady whose shop you looked after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
 And the next door neighbour, they had a little business, her husband had, and I - he used - I used to take him his tea - because he worked all hours, you know, it were only a little firm. And - I always took him his tea every night. And she always - she 
were very good to me. You know - you know, she'd happen give me a copper or she'd buy - and I know at Christmas - she always bought - you know, a birthday and Christmas. She were very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But you didn't have a regular part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What was your first full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Tailoring, I were - we went to learn tailoring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you get this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well me sister worked - there and I went and she were learning - to learn - she learnt me. And then - she got married, as my 
mother always used to say, as one started working one got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What exactly did you have to do in this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I - I had a sewing machine and - and my sister taught me 'til she were married. And then - the husband that she had, his sister,
 took me on. And we went about a month for nothing and then - a month for half a crown. And then we had what we earned.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was that sort of piece work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, when we'd been there about two month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of things were you making?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - trousers. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 Children\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  trousers - little }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 boys\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  trousers for beginning. And then we went onto }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 men\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  and suits and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 That would be very useful all your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, it has. And all me - me sisters were all - worked in - well I'm saying me - all of 
'em - me two oldest sisters, but the oldest sister of all, I never remember her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I think we started at seven. 'Til - twelve. And then - one - 'til five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you work on Sunday or Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we worked Saturday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have a half day at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only Saturday afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any holidays with pay there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh no, not in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you stay there all the time until you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - when I - I did move - to another - firm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Now how long did you stay with this one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I stayed 'til - oh I might have been - eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 What were you paid, you said nothing at first, then half a crown, how much did you usually average when you were on piecework?}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh not much. Well - I don't think it were above eight shilling.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - we thought it was a lot in them days because I - I was supposed to be - pick it up - quick.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh it all went to me mother, when we got a penny in shilling back. Spending money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What would your mother spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Me mother? On - food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you spend your penny on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Penny in the shilling. If we earned six - six - shilling, we - six - got sixpence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What would you spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - there were no pictures or anything like that in then days. It were hair ribbons and sweets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you like pomfret cakes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so. I don't like 'em now but I like 'em - I eat 'em because I think they do me good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you get on with the people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh very well. Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You were on Christian name terms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
YES? I always - I always remember - of course I should be going - turned eighteen then - I once earned nineteen and tenpence. And I asked him if well - if - if I give him tuppence if he'd give me a sovereign, so I could take a sovereign home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 This was your second job was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. 'Course I were older then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you feel about your first employer, the first man you worked for?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well he were more of a concern were that. You know. But the other firm were a private firm. The second one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you feel about the work, did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, I always liked the work. And they were always very good to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When you were about eighteen you moved to another firm doing the same sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. The same sort of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you get this job, why did you change?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I thought that - they were getting more for - for the garments that they made at the other firm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 It was better pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I thought so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And was it a smaller firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But it were a - more of a private firm, all the family worked there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you do exactly the same work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What hours did you work in the second place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any holidays with pay there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What were you paid in the second place, was it just piecework then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES. Same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Once you earned nineteen and ten - did they give you a sovereign?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If I'd - yes, he did do, he said - but - eeh I though it were - it were marvellous taking a poun
d home. I didn't take so many though. I started paying for me board.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you feel it was a fair wage or not at the second place?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - in them days there weren't big wages. I - it were - I were lucky to get that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you give any of that money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh I start - I - I gave her me sovereign, I gave her me - but - I didn't - you know, I wanted more clothes then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You wanted more money back then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 So how much would you give your mother then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I think I gave her about twelve shilling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you buy your own clothes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Own - bought me own clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you get on with the people you worked with at the second job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh very well. Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did your employer treat you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Same, I were - you know, we liked 'em. We called 'em by all their first names and - they call all us with us first names. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any other jobs up to getting married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, I helped in a tea room. That's Saturday afternoon and Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you get this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - it were - people that I knew that lived - by. And they kept asking if I knew anybody that'd go. So me and me friend - we went, because we liked - clothes then, we liked nice clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you have to do in this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
We - used to serve tea to visitors in - that - when - to crags. It were a big old mill that - that had been closed down years and years but it were turned into a - a dance room and a - roller skating and a tearoom.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What hours did you work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - it were only the same as afternoon and then - it were really washing up - after tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You went Saturday and Sunday did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, and holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What were you paid there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh, I don't - oh about two shilling, that were about all. There were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 
no tips}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  in them days. No, not them. We had us tea, we got us tea given.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And you'd be meeting people would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I must have done at them times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you give any of that money to your mother or did you keep it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, that were me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you get on with the people you worked with there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did your employer treat you at the tearoom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you mean them that employed me in tearoom? Oh all right. Oh yes, they were good to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you like them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you feel about the work did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, I liked it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any other jobs at all, have you done any other jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Have you worked since you were married or did you stop when you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Not 'til - my husband went into the Forces.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 1916.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I went back to the - same firm. But they had a branch firm then, and I went back to the branch firm, near - near Halifax.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long did you stay there before you gave it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I stayed there 'til - he were in the Forces thr
ee years. And I stayed there - you know, 'til - and then - I - I gave up working then until - for a year or two and then - he went away working, he were never at home. He used to go all over country and Ireland and - Isle of Man and all over. And - so I w
ent back to work instead of going with him. And I went back to work - at the same job. Same -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When did you retire then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I worked for this firm - well I - I got - I were old, well I got to be manageress, I were manageress twelve year. And I
 - we had about fifty girls sewing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You went full time did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. I went full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How old would you be when you stopped work altogether?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh I should be about forty-three. I put weight on. Oh I did put weight on. And I worked hard
. But I - I put weight on, that's really why I gave up, because I'd a good job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would you have preferred another type of occupation or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so, I always enjoyed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you serve an apprenticeship or training period for you job, you did didn't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES. Just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you belong to any trade union at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different interests
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well the last firm that I worked at - 
he were a snob. YES, he - he were - you know, he were nice with me. And nothing against him in any way but I couldn't - he weren't one that - you could call by his first name or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was this when you went to the branch firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4614584\charrsid13597434 No, this was where I were as manageress.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was this one of their other firms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. But that were in Halifax, it were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you feel there were divisions of interest among workers? Some people feel that; in those days there was a great division bet
ween trained craftsmen and other workers, did you feel that or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so. No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I don't think so. Only it gave you - more - working full time gave you more money didn't it. Well you had more prospects hadn't you.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you continue to live at home when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Or with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you spend Sunday any differently, you went to the tea rooms didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Is that when you stopped going to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you stop going to Sunday school when you left school as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you take an interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You told me earlier something of how you spent your spare time, did you continue to spend your spare time in the same way or did you do di
fferent things now, did you still go for walks and things or not, and did you still belong to the Primrose Club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, I - I started - the Primrose when I were about - seventeen - or eighteen. And - but it were - really a Conservative branch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you still go to the magic lantern now you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 es}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 .

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you go out in the evening now you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - not 'til - you know, we were seven - seventeen or eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where would you go in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You told me about hiding your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If we went to a dance. We used to like to go to a dance. But we daren't let me father know we were going. We used to take us dresse}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  to one of - of us friend}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 s house to put on. And - we used to have wait while }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 a train passed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
- to open door to go in at night, if they were in bed, if me father were in bed. So they wouldn't hear us open door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you near the railway then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, the railway - there were road and then fields and then canal and then railway
. But it - it always seemed to - we knew trains - time of trains. And - you know, many a time - of course we weren't - we didn't go to dances that often, but we knew the - there were a train that - oh we'll go now, we'll - train'll be coming. Get in witho
ut hear - him hearing us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your father ever find out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But your mother knew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh me mother knew, yes, but she wouldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who did you go with to these dances?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Me friend at - one of neighbours children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you go anywhere else at night, apart from dances?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so, only - we had - these 'ere evenings - where we had magic lanterns and - social evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But you'd stopped going to the church hadn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9250902\charrsid13597434 es}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 .

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you make any new friends, boys or girls, at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well only - only them round about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you meet your new friends, how did you get to know people at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I think that - when we were seventeen, sixteen and seventeen - we used to go on what they called parade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Down - between }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 Hebden}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  Bridge and Marrow Road. And - we'd meet lads - you know, boys there and talk to 'em and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever bring your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well not boyfriends, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Girlfriends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, girl friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any special friends at this time, boys or girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You had this special girl friend you went to dances with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any special boyfriends at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, not - so young. Not 'til I got older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How old would you be when you met your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 My husband? Oh I had a few boyfriends before him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How old would you be when you had your first boyfriend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say - seventeen. Or eighteen - seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where would you meet him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 On the walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where did you used to go out with him to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we used to go walks in wood and - but we generally went - a few of us together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your parents meet your friends at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Not the boyfriends, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did they expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we were never late home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes. We were always home soon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What time did you normally have to be back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - before ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When you went to a dance what time would you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we always tried to get home before ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What age were you when you were married?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Twenty-two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long had you known your husband then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we'd - only been courting twelve month. But it were rather - we were married rather sudden. You see, my }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 husband\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
 mother and father died when he was ten. And his oldest sister brought them up. There were four of 'em. Two girls and two boys. Well - the thr
ee - the two boys - and a girl were all courting. So she said - with 'em being courting it looked as if she were going to be left. So she got a house - keeping job. And she got a housekeep - she said she were going to get housekeeping job, and give the ho
u
se - home up, and we could all be married. And so - that'a way - 'cos I'd nothing to be married with. But you see - the - this mother left a nice bit of money. That had brought 'em all up and given 'em all a trade. Well what were left - were shared. There
 wasn't a lot but there were - few hundred each. Well - you see, I - we - we had the house that they lived in, but everything new. We everything made, everything - good. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 This was at Halifax?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And - and that's made us - get married - when we 
did, the two boys got married, the other boy said, well - he were ten year - his wife were ten year older than me and he were older than my husband. But - he said, well, he might as well get married, but they'd arranged their holidays. Two couples of 'em,
 but they weren't - t'other couple were married but they weren't. But anyway - at finish up they arranged that they'd get married - before us and go as a married couple, you know, and they did. And we were married same as six weeks after them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long altogether had you known your husband then when you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I might - I met him at Hardcastle Crags.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 At the caf\'e9 there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. That's how I met him. There used to be about a dozen of 'em come every week. Camping from Halifax. And 
that's - how I met him. Well I'd known him a year or two but we'd gone - we'd gone properly for twelve month. But I'd never been to his home and he'd never been into my home. But we - but anyway when we were going to be married, well - before we arranged 
t
o be married his sister - asked me to go like. And she were ever so good to me. And she said, well I know you're - I hadn't any bottom drawer stuff. 'Cos I - I used to spend all me money on clothes. And - but she said - she were right good, she says, neve
r mind, she said, everything I touch this next month in using I'll write it down. She says, and then - we'll go to warehouse, and we got everything wholesale.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Which warehouse was this?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 In Halifax. But - you'd to buy half a dozen, no less. You know, in brushes and - using things. Blankets, sheets, everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 She bought those for you did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, we paid for 'em ourselves. But - she wrote everything down that I should need. She were right good to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But you bought them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, well I don't 'cos I hadn't any money but - my husband did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You had a good start then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh I had a very good start. Very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Your husband came from Halifax did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you save up money before getting married or not, you didn't did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I didn't. He - he had a bit but not me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your mother help you in setting up home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, well you see me mother couldn't, she hadn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would you say his sister did help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 They all bought me a bit of something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long were you engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't think I were engaged above three month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have a nice ring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh I had a nice - had a nice ring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Could you describe the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - we - we had a - you see I lived at He
bden Bridge. And - we weren't going - we went to Blackpool on us honeymoon but we didn't go while day after. So we had a tea. And - at me new home. And my husband's sisters helped - to make it you know. And -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were you married at Hebden Bridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 No, I were married at - at King Cross, Halifax.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of a church was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
A church. Church of England. No, a Church of England. And we'd a nice quiet wedding but - we had about - ten, you know, and we had a - we had a piano and we had a player. And I suppose we sung and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you stay there that night then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 We stayed there that night. And then we went to Blackpool - morning after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was it just family who came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, just the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have many presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Y
es, I - I think I did right nicely. With neighbours and work - them that I worked with and - yes, and - my husband had a few friends in Halifax. Yes, I - we did very nicely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What did you wear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I had a cream costume and a lovely hat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of a hat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 A black hat with osprey feathers, I can see myself now. Yes, I had a cream costume.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you carry any flowers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I've forgot if - we should happen just have a - I don't think I had a bought or anything, I think it was just a - a button hole.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What was the first address you lived at at Halifax?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Belmont Place, Parkinson Lane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How many years did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I was married in 1911 and Dora were born - in 1913. And then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you move before the end of the war or after?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
No, it were after - it were before, yes. And then - I had a friend that - that had a house with a sitting room and we hadn't a sitting room. We'd a nice living room and big kitchen. And cellar to wash in. But we'd no - oh 
it was cellar kitchen but - we didn't live in it - cellar kitchen. And I wanted a sitting room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How old would Dora be when you moved then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And I think Dora would be about four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 So that's about 1917 then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh no, it were afore then. She
'd happen only be three. Because - and we - we got this house next to a friend of mine. In - in Parkinson Lane, same. But higher up. And then - we hadn't been there long when he had to join Forces. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 And me and Dora lived there on us own. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But I went back to work. I went back to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 So at the end of the war you were still living in this second house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Yes. But - I didn't live there long because - oh - somebody bought it over me head. And I had to - oh every night when I got home there were letters 
- saying I'd have to get out, I'd have to get out. And at finish up I did get out. And I got a nice house with a bath. But bath were in kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When would this be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 That's be - Jim were in t'Army. I should say it'd be - 1916, would it be. YES? W
ell - well I weren't there long, I weren't - I - might be at latter end of year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where did you move to this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Then we - we moved - it were a lovely house - just above Halifax infirmary. But - oh we had poor health. Both me and Dora were alwa
ys - he were in the Army then, he didn't know. About me remove - well he'd know I were removed, he didn't know where it was or anything. But - oh we had poor heath. So - we stopped there though 'til he were demobbed. Well he were demobbed in 1920. YES.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you know the address of this one near the infirmary?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Emscott Avenue. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 Emscott}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 . Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How old was your husband when you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Twenty-five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What was his job?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 A joiner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he have any other jobs before he became a joiner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 NA.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he have any other jobs after he became a joiner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 He was always a joiner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh he - yes, he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 He went in the Army in between?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. And then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 That was 1916 to 1920 he was in the Army, then what did he do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well he didn't do anything 'til he were poorly years and then if - he did a bit of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 fire watching}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 , but that were in the second world war. Well that won't be - in this will it. No, he only did a bit of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 fire watching}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  because he were poorly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was this after he'd stopped being a joiner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES? Well he was too poorly to go back to his own job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When did he stop being a joiner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well he - he didn't give it up, he were poorly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - well he's been dead twenty-two years, and he were poorly ten - off and on. That's thirty-two in't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he ever do any other casual or part time jobs when he was a joiner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You worked a bit after you were married in 1916, how did your husband feel about you working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well, I didn't go to work 'til he went in the Forces. But you see I'd only twelve and six a week, and five shilling for her. And I was the only - tradesman - he was the only tradesman on our street - and I was the only one - that didn't get 
the wages made up. They all worked for - same as Mackintoshes, Post Office, or -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And they made their wages up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And they all made their wages up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who did your husband work for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Joiner in - in Halifax.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who did he work for, was it a small firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, it were a big firm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But they didn't make his wage up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, never a penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did he feel about you working then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well he didn't like the idea because of her being young. But - I did it - to - to live really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How do you think your husband felt about his work, did he like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh he liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was Dora the only child you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Could I have her date of birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Seventeenth of February, 1913.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was she born at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. I had a private nurse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you know what to expect in childbirth and how did you get on when you had her, did you know what to expect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 We-l - I did and I didn't as you might say. But I were - I were all right, I had a nice - had a nic
e confinement but a poor beginning. Very poorly for - three - four month. Yes. But I were all right - at the end. And I got over it all right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any medical help, you had a private nurse you say, was she with you all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Only during the day. She didn't live in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who helped with the actual confinement?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we had a midwife and her. And a doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would you say you knew what to expect then or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I - I don't think I really did. But - you've a bit of an idea haven't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your husband help at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh not in the room but - he stayed off work. I know he made the nurse - meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How soon were you out of bed after having Dora?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh I - I was - I should say - oh out of bed - I should say a fortnight. And then another fortnight - not doing anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 So how long would it be before you had a whole day out of bed would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I should say about - twelve or - twelve days or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you manage while you were in bed, who helped to look after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well I had - the nurse looked after me, and then we had a - a lady came in to do the washing, and just tidy up. But she weren't there long, only the washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How many weeks did she come for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 A month. Four weeks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long did you have the nurse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, she came -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did any of your relations or neighbours help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - no, they came in and brought me - bit of luxuries. That was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 This lady who came in just did the washing?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What exactly did the nurse do for you during the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - she'd - she'd make the meal - the - the midday meal, and the tea, and she'd wash up after it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You just had her for a month?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Just during the day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you feed Dora?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh I - she had the breast. For - I should say - seven or eight month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you enjoy feeding her that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well it was there, I had it. I - I had the milk you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any difficulties in feeding her at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If you needed advice about Dora who did you ask?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't think I had - any need really, I don't remember -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If the baby was sleeping would you wake her for a feed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If she cried before the normal time would you feed her then early?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well if she cried I'd pick her up. And if I thought that it was - how long it was since she had her feed well - if it weren't long I didn't, but if it were - an hour or so I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did she ever not seem hungry, what would you do if she didn't seem hungry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, she never seemed -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long did you let her go on feeding at a time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I couldn't tell you. Until sometimes she'd dropped off to sleep or -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 About how long would it be, have you any idea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say ten minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 At each side or just ten minutes altogether?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Ten minutes altogether should think. Well - mightn't be so long sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You had plenty of milk did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When did you first give her solid food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 Well I daresay she - she had Cow and Gate milk when she were about - eight - seven or eight month old. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 In between. You know, then - she kept having - of course there weren't that baby food that there is today then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When would she first have anything solid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say she'd be - ten month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you wean her gradually then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did she mind, did it unsettle her at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you think at that time that it did any harm to a baby to let it cry or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh well - well - I - we never let her cry. No. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever punish her when she was a baby if she was naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I don't think I did, I don't think she were ever naughty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How much did your husband have to do
 with Dora when she was a baby under a year old, did he have anything to do with her, did he ever feed her or bath her or change her nappy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh no, no. No. He played with her but - yes, yes, but not - actually - did anything in that line.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he ever help to get her to sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, he'd take her to bed and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would he go to her in the night if she needed attention or was that your job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't - I think that - it were my job really but - I don't - she was a good child. She were a good child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he ever take her out when she was a baby without you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where would he take her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 He'd take her in the park in the pram.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you know what your husband earned when you were first married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How much of that would he give to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - he - he earned - his - his wage then - when we were married were about thirty-three shilling, and I - he gave me about twenty - six, and - what he kept - were for his dinners, and - his clothes. Well I mean - oh he were always good that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you discuss with your husband how the money should be spent, did you both talk about how the money should be spent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, he left it all to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You had a few years in Belmont Place didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Place. Belmont Place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How many rooms were there in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 There were - two bedrooms, an attic bedroom and a nice living room and a nice kitchen and a cellar to wash in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any relatives or lodgers living with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any paid help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you do the washing at home or was it sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I - I did it at - myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you mend or make the clothes for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, I made - Dora's - all Dora's clothes and me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you mend the clothes too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were the clothes new or secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 New.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember where you bought them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I couldn't tell you now, I - Halifax,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you know when Dora had new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh she were always - I was always making her - you know, always - always making her dresses and coats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about shoes, did your husband mend the shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you all have new shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Any particular time when you had shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. Oh - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Just when you needed them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did your husband help with the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Or cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I were always well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he help with the washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he light the fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, he looked after the fires and brought the coal in and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he do any decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who did that, did you do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, paid for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he do any repairs or improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes - he did - odd jobs in the house, in his own line. Joinering. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of things did he do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - I couldn't tell you now only - he'd see to the window cords and see to the - window bottoms that were all - you know - if they were - any breakage or anything he'd - he'd repair 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 A handy man to have around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
