\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever bottle any fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were the vegetables and fruit you had grown or did you buy them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 We bought them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
