\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who taught her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Me.
