\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, we went to the - there were - pictures then. We went to the pictures.
