\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, only flowers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any other interests outside the home, did you have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - not - not in - not before '18. But after - we started going to whist drives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Before 1918 did you ever go out just to enjoy yourself, without your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did anyone outside the home help you look after your house and family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Any relations, friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 If you were confined to bed how did you manage, were you ever in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Never ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did either of you have any relatives living nearby and how much did you see of them, which relatives lived near you when you wer
e married in Halifax?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, me sister-in-laws. We were always very friendly with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How much would you see of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well one of them we saw nearly every day. But she others - casual you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where would you see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - she used to visit us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Just the one particular one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Her that brought them - him up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Where would you see the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - we'd go - either visit their house and they'd visit ours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How often would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh any time. And never a went a week, never went a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You say you had plenty of friends, where did you see your friends at Halifax?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - when we went on the moor and - you see there's a big moor at Halifax by the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 infirmary}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  there. We used to go on there a ter
rible lot. And when - we were - when Dora were little, we used to be - a lot of mothers used to go and take children, and we'd take a bit of lunch. And have it there. And play on the - on - were - were called the moor but it were - really on roadside.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you and your husband share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - yes. They were through him that I got to know them. With knowing their husband. Yes, he - 'cos I were - I were new to Halifax you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have any friends of your own that weren't friends of your husband's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did he have any friends of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you invite friends into the home, how often would you have friends into the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh well, we did a - a nice bit of - entertaining. If you call it entertaining. Just having - a couple in. And then we'd go back.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How often would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh well - should say nearly every other week, were - one another - not at one house every other week but - we used to visit - you
 know, his friend and then they'd come back and then - we - were always friendly with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink when they came to visit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we always had a nice tea but - we never had any drink in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would it be on any particular day or occasion when they came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Would you say that the friends invited in were your husband's friends or friends that you both shared?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well they were really his friends at beginning. But then - they were mine and all after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did friends ever call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I don't say every week, but - any time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did neighbours ever call in, did your neighbours just pop in or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - they'd come in - happen for half an hour or - in afternoon or - or if they want - if they were going to the shop, to see if I could - if they could bring anything and I used to do same with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You did go out to visit friends and neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what did you do when you got together with friends and neighbours, did you ever make music or play games?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so, it were mostly - if we did we played - we had hand at cards. Game - whist - or solo.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You were good at that were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, we used to like to play cards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was your home rented at Halifax?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you see anything of the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, he came - I don't know - every month. For the rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did you feel about him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh he were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 In Halifax who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well there were - there were a lot of important people. I should say - same as - them that had Firths carpet }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 mill}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434  and Mollie Rayton Cleggs, the big mill owners. There were a terrible lot of big mills in Halifax.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever come into contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Why do you think they were considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - they always seemed - to be at top of list if there were anything going. Invitations and - you know, and giving. Giving to charities and such as that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about the shopkeepers, who did they associate with, who did the shopkeepers at Halifax have for friends, did you ever notice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I didn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about the clergy, who did they have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I couldn't really tell you, only - they'd have - the big nuts that went to church.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 The same people you mentioned before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Who did the teachers have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Teachers? Well it depend - which school they were at, because we used to have a teacher - ob but that'd be after 1918. We used to have a teacher that come but she were interested in Guides. And Dora were in Guides, but that'd be after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Before 1918 did you ever notice who they had for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, unless - it depend what all - you know, which school they were at and - and what they were interested in outside of school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about the farmers at Halifax, who did they have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - I couldn't tell you only - I don't think they'd ever any time to associate with anybody. Only their own family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What about the employers, all these mill owners, who would they have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh - they'd have same as them. You know, same - you know, there were a terrible lot of mills in Halifax.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of mills were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 All sorts. Carpets - everything, they mad
e everything in Halifax. Toffee, Chocolate. Carpets. Oh - jewellery. There were everything I think. Made what you could mention nearly were manufactured in Halifax - in them days. Even cigars.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 It's not a very big place is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, and they never seemed any of 'em were poor. They all - they all seemed. -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you never see any poor people in Halifax in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 Well there were plenty of poor people but they didn't live - where I lived, there were no poor people - there were working cla
ss people by me but - never anybody - what you might say poor, but I think it makes a lot of difference when I thought about my family. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
When they're a big family they're bound to be poor. To a certain extent, aren't they. But families that's only one or tw
o - well - they look on - down on them with a big family, don't they. But - I think many a time - we were never well off, and my mother never owed a ha'penny. But we'd never - anything left. At end of week. And I think it were with being a big family. It 
w
eren't really because we were poor. It were - that's what I think. I've thought about me life since I've started on this, and I thought well, we had us god days. Oh is it on. You know, we had us good days, but we should also - me mother'd also have her an
x
ious - to clothe us. But we were lucky in one way. They were all sewers. That were a big help. And I always remember - me father always dressed the boys. He always bought all the boys - the three boys - 'cos the youngest'd be - the other - two oldest, he 
a
lways - dressed them, and they were always dressed nice. And he always paid for that. Himself. Well I think many a time - we might have been looked on by some folk as being poor, but it weren't - it was really because we'd a big family. Yes, it - it does 
m
ake - but we've never lived in up n' down. House and bedroom like a lot of people. Like a terrible lot of people that - that had families that lived in them sort of houses. In them days. But we'd always a different bedroom. We had no bath or anything like
 that in them days. But - we had other things. That made us - just that bit - independent as you might say.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What sort of people would you say went to church in Halifax in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well I should say mixed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 And to chapel, were there any difference in the people who went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No. No, the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Where you lived did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups in Halifax?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I think - they'd all a nice standard of living - that lived round about -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was there any particularly poor are in Halifax?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh yes, but - yes, there were - mostly in the centre. Around the centre.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Could you describe what sort of occupations the people would have who lived in the one up and downs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well they were mostly labourers. You know, and - and there were a terrible lot of families - well there is in Brighouse if it comes to that. I've been astonished when I've got talking to people - and said where they lived 
and where they were born. And how many there were in a family with a house and bedroom. I thought, well, we're in a big family but we never had that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How did they all manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 I don't know, I often wonder that. But they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you think that one group of the working class felt itself superior to the rest?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well they were very mixed. You know, there were - some - I don't think - they ever kept theirself to theirself, them that thought they were better. I think that they were mostly - as
 you might say mixed, but picked their own friends in their own - station.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Were some families thought of as rough and others as respectable in Halifax?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well they were mixed, they were - in this lower part of town - there were some rough ones. Es
pecially among the Irish. A lot - a terrible lot of Irish. And - they were very rough were some of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 In what way were they rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Getting drunk and - getting into fights and - they were always - the paper - you know, you read it in the paper
 about 'em. You didn't live near them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No, I don't think so, they were both - rough in both labourer and craftsmanship.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever have a struggle to make ends meet at that time when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 No - I've been very lucky that way. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 
He - he had a bit of - he used to have - be}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13597434  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8149107\charrsid13597434 unemployed in the winter. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
It were always round about December to - March. When he was working in - the building trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Was this when you were first married or after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 It - when we were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well how did you manage then then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we always managed because - we'd always that little bit - on one side.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What difference did it make when your husband was ill or out of work, was he ever ill in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well - well he - he were never out of work. He were never ill. And he were just out of work in the wintertime when he was in the building trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 But you had enough put by to carry on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES? We always managed. We were careful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you ever get help from the Guardians, the Parish or any charities?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you say he thought he might get help from the union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 He'd get a bit for the union, a few shilling, but it wouldn't be much. It'd get a - he'd get a bit when - from the union I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Do you remember how much he would get?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, I don't think he'd get - above eight shilling. Something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What were you telling me about going to the spiritualist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well we used to go to the caf\'e9
 at Saturday afternoon. And then when we'd had us - we used to have an hour then at spiritualists. I weren't a spiritualist, but it were just somewhere to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How many people went, how many people were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh there'd be a - a big circle there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
Well I don't think anything really - happened. They never told me anything. But some people - they went in like a trance and - sometimes and - and they'd - tell people - what were going to happen or wh
at had happened. But they never - I never remember 'em ever coming to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 What made you go, why did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well - we used to wonder about us husbands, if they were - living a straight life like we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 You wanted second sight to find out did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes. But anyway we never got to know. We trusted 'em. And I think they were right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 How long did you go on going to this spiritualist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Oh we didn't go every week, only ever now and again at Saturday after we'd had us tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you have to pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Yes, but not much, it were only - a copper, it wouldn't be - it weren't much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did you take Dora with you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3764008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Did she like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1910858 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 Well, she sat on me knee, I think she'd go to sleep. I don't think she were interested in what they were - doing.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-461\li461\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid3764008 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1538111\charrsid13597434 
\par }}